{"tid":1682702,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國蛋/湖北蛋/日本蛋，邊隻好食D？","createTime":"2019-10-30T08:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T03:56:30.000Z","uid":89349,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e1735bb5905913e3451956c760104458e69dd0","tid":1682702,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTAkiMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTAkiMr.png&h=8b930377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁都唔撚係謀殺係乜？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">身邊有個差佬朋友，一大班人食飯果陣大大聲話無問題，立即俾人屌到反皮。<br />\n條友之後屈服，，笑笑口話講笑姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食屎啦屌你老母Ya Mi Mi</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(難怪立即俾人放上老豆搵仔啦)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n正題<br />\n日本蛋其實係買佢信心，我唔覺有咩特別好食。反而湖北蛋食落去又幾香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2ed44c0e350e78ce5050f716026ed611ab1c56","tid":1682702,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1533201815358e16a2c7ac2627ad54bf9c1f7ebe","tid":1682702,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"聽聞泰國蛋多菌 日本蛋貴 但我食唔出分別 <br />\n個人鐘意美國蛋 夠滑<br />\n支那蛋就應該隻隻差唔多"},{"pid":"ce139dbddf5ffba989e70c8d40189a311c4a9e1a","tid":1682702,"uid":6864,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1533201815358e16a2c7ac2627ad54bf9c1f7ebe","tid":1682702,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"聽聞泰國蛋多菌 日本蛋貴 但我食唔出分別 <br />\n個人鐘意美國蛋 夠滑<br />\n支那蛋就應該隻隻差唔多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"日本蛋顏色特別黃，炒蛋出黎會好靚，蛋味都幾香濃。 <br />\n<br />\n美國蛋係大隻d，蛋白比例相對高d，顏色比較淡，用黎整其他野對顏色比較敏感係比較啱用"},{"pid":"61975c4f59cabd280c61f35f54ad4987c8252cd4","tid":1682702,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"日本蛋仲貴過美國蛋"},{"pid":"4fe2b6f8d42295c4de6d0f1acac3ab651a0f52ef","tid":1682702,"uid":21757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n只敢食日本蛋"},{"pid":"baeddd2c1d46ee8e6d52dd643d106bc8249f2362","tid":1682702,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"日本蛋蛋味重啲"},{"pid":"9a94ec6081e1d0951f8b7b0c0a74cb25de93e61a","tid":1682702,"uid":89349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"baeddd2c1d46ee8e6d52dd643d106bc8249f2362","tid":1682702,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"日本蛋蛋味重啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:10:33.000Z","msg":"如果做糖心蛋，用日本蛋係安全啲"},{"pid":"06cbbe93ea4d738e7aab8f66e940e20019c690a1","tid":1682702,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"泰國蛋便宜<br />\n30蚊有30隻"},{"pid":"81a94aeefa6f213412982d6f2dc35c30c9c33814","tid":1682702,"uid":2146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"屋企支那蛋同日本蛋都有買 但我食唔出分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a53d53de60c15fdc47dc390926ed01aa5fa2a4","tid":1682702,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81a94aeefa6f213412982d6f2dc35c30c9c33814","tid":1682702,"uid":2146,"like":1,"disl